{"tid":1160884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正能量］大家仲記唔記得自己既夢想","createTime":"2019-05-18T18:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T03:00:16.000Z","uid":64554,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9e818ad5ffa0a9f87baae96a348741d78de0a586","tid":1160884,"uid":64554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"細個果陣一定有寫過「我的志願」呢個topic<br />\n<br />\n但係讀完書或者出到黎社會工作既你，又有冇朝住自己既夢想推進呢？<br />\n<br />\n抑或而經成為左一個唔會實現到既夢？<br />\n個個都話，香港地，唔好學人講夢想。<br />\n<br />\n有人為左兩餐，放棄左夢想<br />\n有人為左屋企人/另一半，放棄左夢想<br />\n有人因為懶，放棄左夢想<br />\n<br />\n夢想並唔係遙不可及，但唔一定會實現到。<br />\n但至少，我諗你一定要傻過，癲過，失敗過，先知道為夢想而打拼係點既一回事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會冇夢想，咁你就要為自己諗一個夢想，去豐富自己人生既意義。<br />\n<br />\n無論你係為夢想打拼緊，為生活打拼緊，追夢或追唔到夢，都留底你既夢想或者你既難處，如果你成功左既話都留底你既故事，為呢個post既過路人打打氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我係呢到為各位有夢想既人講一聲加油，you will be greatest ever! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af76bdce440af7f264d2a114fa0afe8dd6ac459c","tid":1160884,"uid":64554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"希望呢個post唔好咁快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf69a2904e14bee1deffecb0c81799dd398bb204","tid":1160884,"uid":1554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:31:06.000Z","msg":"嗰時好似話要做設計師同消防員<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd26aa1bd210